ay, however, that I was pleasantly surprised. I’ve used this card 3 times now and 2 of the 3 times it gave me a price that was lower than my insurance copay.</p><cite><strong>Jose,&nbsp;Drug Discount Customer</strong></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How to Use This Benefit</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tell your pharmacy either in person or over the phone that your member ID number is&nbsp;<strong>DDN6686&nbsp;</strong>and your BIN number is&nbsp;<strong>015558</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can also go&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.discountdrugnetwork.com/drug-pricing/\"><strong>online</strong></a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<strong>call us at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:877-537-5537\">1-(877) 537-5537</a></strong>&nbsp;to look up discounted prescription prices to find out if another pharmacy in your area has even lower prices. Simply enter your prescription drug name in the search tool to find out who has the lowest price for your prescription.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"legal-assistance\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Legal Assistance</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":194,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-legal.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"accident-support\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Accident Support</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":302,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-accident-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-302\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"vision\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Vision</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":155,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-vision.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-155\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"dental\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Dental</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":182,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-dental.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-182\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Benefits','','inherit','closed','closed','','300-revision-v1','','','2020-08-27 17:28:26','2020-08-27 22:28:26','',300,'http://drivers-benefits.local/news/300-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (313,2,'2020-08-27 17:30:42','2020-08-27 22:30:42','<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"telemedicine\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\">Telemedicine</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":168,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-telemedicine.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-168\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All drivers and their families can speak to a doctor for free in their language by phone, secure online video, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>&nbsp;for a non-emergency consultation – anytime, anywhere. Paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Free 24/7 calls and video conferencing with board-certified doctors</li><li>Translators available in 150 languages</li><li>Doctors can call in your prescriptions (no controlled substances)</li><li>Doctors can diagnose and treat non-emergency conditions including:<ul><li>Allergies</li><li>Cough and sore throat</li><li>Cold/Flu</li><li>Fever</li><li>Nausea and vomiting</li><li>Rash</li><li>And more!</li></ul></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Who Qualifies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Black Car drivers in New York are eligible for telemedicine, paid for by The Black Car Fund</li><li>In order to start using your benefits, you’ll need to provide some basic information, such as your name and Taxi and Limousine Commission (TLC) license number –&nbsp;<a href=\"https://driversbenefits.org/activate-now/?utm_source=WB&amp;utm_medium=Telemed\">Activate your benefits</a></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“Such an easy and affordable process – within 15 minutes I had registered my account, scheduled the appointment, consulted with the doctor on the phone, and received the Rx I needed to treat my infection.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>– Heather, MDLive Customer</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How to Use This Benefit</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>How does it work?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First, you must call&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>&nbsp;or go online to activate your Telemedicine benefit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>It’s Safe</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Telemedicine gives you access to board-certified doctors with more than 15 years of experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What services are available?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Telemedicine doctors can diagnose and treat a number of health issues, including allergies, asthma, the flu, cold, arthritis, backaches, joint pain, and much more. Prescriptions can be phoned in to whatever pharmacy is most convenient for you. While the call with the doctor is free, you will be responsible for the cost of any medications you need, or for any doctors visits&nbsp;you may need for situations an MDLIVE doctor can’t solve over the phone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Is my family covered?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes. Our telemedicine benefit is not for only our hard-working drivers, but for their families as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"classes\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\">Classes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":190,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-classes.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-190\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We connect you to free safety and health &amp; wellness classes that will help you become a better driver. Drivers get paid $300 to complete the Defensive Driving Class every three years and they get a one-time payment of $150 to complete The Black Car Fund Wellness, Safety, and Education (STEP) Program.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Several free classes are available at The Black Car Fund Wellness Center and the Independent Drivers Guild throughout the year</li><li>Drivers get paid $300 to complete the Defensive Driving Class every three years.</li><li>Drivers get a one-time payment of $150 to complete The Black Car Fund Wellness, Safety and Education (STEP) Program.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Who Qualifies</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>All drivers located in New York State are eligible to use this benefit</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>How to Use This Benefit</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Call us at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>&nbsp;to sign up for any of the following classes:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Eligible drivers receive $300 to take the Taxi and Limousine Commission (TLC)-mandated Defensive Driving Class through The Black Car Fund.</li><li>Eligible drivers receive $150 to take The Black Car Fund Wellness, Safety and Education (STEP) Program through The Black Car Fund. The wellness course is designed to help drivers improve their physical and mental health on the road.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many other classes are available from the Independent Drivers Guild to drivers throughout the year, including:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>5-star Professional Service: learn how to get more 5-Star reviews from customers</li><li>24-hour Universal License: get your Taxi and Limousine Commission license</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"drivers-support\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\">Drivers Support</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":186,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-support.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-186\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>What is Driver Support?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Driver Support is access to free 45-minute sessions with licensed professionals via phone and video to Drivers Benefits members, through MDLIVE. These professionals will listen to any problems you are facing and help you work through them. They can help you address:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Stress about work, money, etc.</li><li>Worry or concern over major life changes</li><li>Sadness over a loss</li><li>Issues with family</li><li>Feelings of panic</li><li>Working through addictions</li><li><strong>And more</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Who Qualifies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Drivers Benefits members are able to use Driver Support, thanks to The Black Car Fund</li><li>Not a Drivers Benefits member yet? No problem! To start using your benefits, you’ll just need to provide some basic information, like your name and Taxi and Limousine Commission (TLC) license number OR your drivers license.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://driversbenefits.org/activate-now/?utm_source=WB&amp;utm_medium=Telemed\">Activate your benefits here.&nbsp;</a></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How to Use This Benefit</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Driver Support allows you to select the professional you’d like to work with and schedule a time to speak with them within 3-5 days of your request.&nbsp;<strong>Driver Support is not an immediate service and should not be used for emergencies.*</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>First, make sure you activate your MDLIVE account by calling&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://members.mdlive.com/driversdoc/landing_home\">go online</a>&nbsp;to activate your MDLIVE account.</li><li>Download the MDLIVE App (<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mdlive.mobile&amp;hl=en_US\">Google</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mdlive/id839671393#?platform=iphone\">Apple</a>) or&nbsp;<a href=\"http://mdlive.com/driversdoc\">go online</a>&nbsp;to schedule an appointment.<ul><li>Select “Therapy Counseling” at the prompt.</li><li>Complete the health history questions</li><li>Under “Find a Therapist”, you can:<ul><li>Sort by language, availability, or specialty</li><li>Pick the therapist you’d like to use and pick your appointment slot.</li></ul></li><li>Confirm your appointment</li></ul></li><li>When it’s time for your appointment, you’ll receive a text message with the link to the platform.</li><li>After your appointment, schedule a follow-up!<ul><li>Select the same therapist, or find a new one!</li></ul></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>*If you are in need of immediate counsel, please call NYC Well at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel: 1-888-692-9355\">1-888-692-9355.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Need help with translation?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Call us at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel: 1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>&nbsp;and Drivers Benefits can connect you with a translator to help schedule your appointment, and MDLIVE will provide a translator to interpret during your therapy session.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Why Use Driver Support?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Driver Support allows you to address your concerns with a professional, for free, in a convenient and private setting so that you can manage feelings of stress, deal with lifestyle changes, or simply get help coping with you day-to-day problems.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Other Resources</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drivers in the New York City area can also take advantage of the in-person counseling services offered at the IDG Wellness and Counseling Center in Woodside, Queens. Their counselors also provide help with applying for financial resources and public benefits like food stamps, health insurance or housing, etc. Our call center can help you learn more, call them at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel: 1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"prescriptions\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\">Prescriptions</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":198,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-prescriptions.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-198\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Save up to 85% on prescription medications for you or a member of your family. Simply share your member ID number with your local pharmacy in person or over the phone. Provided by the&nbsp;<strong>Independent Drivers Guild.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Save up to 85% on medications that you and your family use every day. It works with or without insurance.</li><li>Simply present your discount card at your local pharmacy and save on prescriptions now and into the future.</li><li>Your discount card is accepted at over 65,000 pharmacies.</li><li>Pay the lowest available price at the register; cardholders save an average of $200 per year!</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Who Qualifies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>All drivers located in New York State are eligible to use this benefit.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>It’s hard to believe something free could be legit. I must say, however, that I was pleasantly surprised. I’ve used this card 3 times now and 2 of the 3 times it gave me a price that was lower than my insurance copay.</p><cite><strong>Jose,&nbsp;Drug Discount Customer</strong></cite></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How to Use This Benefit</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tell your pharmacy either in person or over the phone that your member ID number is&nbsp;<strong>DDN6686&nbsp;</strong>and your BIN number is&nbsp;<strong>015558</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can also go&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.discountdrugnetwork.com/drug-pricing/\"><strong>online</strong></a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<strong>call us at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:877-537-5537\">1-(877) 537-5537</a></strong>&nbsp;to look up discounted prescription prices to find out if another pharmacy in your area has even lower prices. Simply enter your prescription drug name in the search tool to find out who has the lowest price for your prescription.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"legal-assistance\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\">Legal Assistance</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":194,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-legal.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"accident-support\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\">Accident Support</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":302,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-accident-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-302\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"vision\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\">Vision</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":155,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-vision.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-155\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefit__benefit_shadow\" id=\"dental\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefit__benefit_title_shadow\">Dental</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":182,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefit__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-dental.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-182\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Benefits','','inherit','closed','closed','','300-revision-v1','','','2020-08-27 17:30:42','2020-08-27 22:30:42','',300,'http://drivers-benefits.local/news/300-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (314,2,'2020-08-27 17:48:26','2020-08-27 22:48:26','<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefits__benefit_shadow\" id=\"telemedicine\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefits__benefit_title_shadow\">Telemedicine</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":168,\"width\":62,\"height\":100,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized benefits__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-telemedicine.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-168\" width=\"62\" height=\"100\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All drivers and their families can speak to a doctor for free in their language by phone, secure online video, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>&nbsp;for a non-emergency consultation – anytime, anywhere. Paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Free 24/7 calls and video conferencing with board-certified doctors</li><li>Translators available in 150 languages</li><li>Doctors can call in your prescriptions (no controlled substances)</li><li>Doctors can diagnose and treat non-emergency conditions including:<ul><li>Allergies</li><li>Cough and sore throat</li><li>Cold/Flu</li><li>Fever</li><li>Nausea and vomiting</li><li>Rash</li><li>And more!</li></ul></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Who Qualifies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Black Car drivers in New York are eligible for telemedicine, paid for by The Black Car Fund</li><li>In order to start using your benefits, you’ll need to provide some basic information, such as your name and Taxi and Limousine Commission (TLC) license number –&nbsp;<a href=\"https://driversbenefits.org/activate-now/?utm_source=WB&amp;utm_medium=Telemed\">Activate your benefits</a></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“Such an easy and affordable process – within 15 minutes I had registered my account, scheduled the appointment, consulted with the doctor on the phone, and received the Rx I needed to treat my infection.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>– Heather, MDLive Customer</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How to Use This Benefit</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>How does it work?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First, you must call&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>&nbsp;or go online to activate your Telemedicine benefit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>It’s Safe</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Telemedicine gives you access to board-certified doctors with more than 15 years of experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What services are available?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Telemedicine doctors can diagnose and treat a number of health issues, including allergies, asthma, the flu, cold, arthritis, backaches, joint pain, and much more. Prescriptions can be phoned in to whatever pharmacy is most convenient for you. While the call with the doctor is free, you will be responsible for the cost of any medications you need, or for any doctors visits&nbsp;you may need for situations an MDLIVE doctor can’t solve over the phone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Is my family covered?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes. Our telemedicine benefit is not for only our hard-working drivers, but for their families as well.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefits__benefit_shadow\" id=\"classes\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefits__benefit_title_shadow\">Classes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":190,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefits__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-classes.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-190\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We connect you to free safety and health &amp; wellness classes that will help you become a better driver. Drivers get paid $300 to complete the Defensive Driving Class every three years and they get a one-time payment of $150 to complete The Black Car Fund Wellness, Safety, and Education (STEP) Program.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Several free classes are available at The Black Car Fund Wellness Center and the Independent Drivers Guild throughout the year</li><li>Drivers get paid $300 to complete the Defensive Driving Class every three years.</li><li>Drivers get a one-time payment of $150 to complete The Black Car Fund Wellness, Safety and Education (STEP) Program.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Who Qualifies</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>All drivers located in New York State are eligible to use this benefit</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>How to Use This Benefit</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Call us at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>&nbsp;to sign up for any of the following classes:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Eligible drivers receive $300 to take the Taxi and Limousine Commission (TLC)-mandated Defensive Driving Class through The Black Car Fund.</li><li>Eligible drivers receive $150 to take The Black Car Fund Wellness, Safety and Education (STEP) Program through The Black Car Fund. The wellness course is designed to help drivers improve their physical and mental health on the road.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many other classes are available from the Independent Drivers Guild to drivers throughout the year, including:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>5-star Professional Service: learn how to get more 5-Star reviews from customers</li><li>24-hour Universal License: get your Taxi and Limousine Commission license</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefits__benefit_shadow\" id=\"drivers-support\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefits__benefit_title_shadow\">Drivers Support</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":186,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefits__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-support.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-186\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Stressed out? We can help. Drivers Benefits members can speak with a licensed professional for free in their language by secure online video, through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdlive.com/driversdoc\">MDLIVE App</a>. Offered by MDLIVE and paid for by&nbsp;<strong>The Black Car Fund.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>What is Driver Support?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Driver Support is access to free 45-minute sessions with licensed professionals via phone and video to Drivers Benefits members, through MDLIVE. These professionals will listen to any problems you are facing and help you work through them. They can help you address:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Stress about work, money, etc.</li><li>Worry or concern over major life changes</li><li>Sadness over a loss</li><li>Issues with family</li><li>Feelings of panic</li><li>Working through addictions</li><li><strong>And more</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Who Qualifies</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Drivers Benefits members are able to use Driver Support, thanks to The Black Car Fund</li><li>Not a Drivers Benefits member yet? No problem! To start using your benefits, you’ll just need to provide some basic information, like your name and Taxi and Limousine Commission (TLC) license number OR your drivers license.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://driversbenefits.org/activate-now/?utm_source=WB&amp;utm_medium=Telemed\">Activate your benefits here.&nbsp;</a></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How to Use This Benefit</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Driver Support allows you to select the professional you’d like to work with and schedule a time to speak with them within 3-5 days of your request.&nbsp;<strong>Driver Support is not an immediate service and should not be used for emergencies.*</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>First, make sure you activate your MDLIVE account by calling&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://members.mdlive.com/driversdoc/landing_home\">go online</a>&nbsp;to activate your MDLIVE account.</li><li>Download the MDLIVE App (<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mdlive.mobile&amp;hl=en_US\">Google</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mdlive/id839671393#?platform=iphone\">Apple</a>) or&nbsp;<a href=\"http://mdlive.com/driversdoc\">go online</a>&nbsp;to schedule an appointment.<ul><li>Select “Therapy Counseling” at the prompt.</li><li>Complete the health history questions</li><li>Under “Find a Therapist”, you can:<ul><li>Sort by language, availability, or specialty</li><li>Pick the therapist you’d like to use and pick your appointment slot.</li></ul></li><li>Confirm your appointment</li></ul></li><li>When it’s time for your appointment, you’ll receive a text message with the link to the platform.</li><li>After your appointment, schedule a follow-up!<ul><li>Select the same therapist, or find a new one!</li></ul></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>*If you are in need of immediate counsel, please call NYC Well at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel: 1-888-692-9355\">1-888-692-9355.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Need help with translation?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Call us at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel: 1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>&nbsp;and Drivers Benefits can connect you with a translator to help schedule your appointment, and MDLIVE will provide a translator to interpret during your therapy session.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Why Use Driver Support?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Driver Support allows you to address your concerns with a professional, for free, in a convenient and private setting so that you can manage feelings of stress, deal with lifestyle changes, or simply get help coping with you day-to-day problems.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Other Resources</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Drivers in the New York City area can also take advantage of the in-person counseling services offered at the IDG Wellness and Counseling Center in Woodside, Queens. Their counselors also provide help with applying for financial resources and public benefits like food stamps, health insurance or housing, etc. Our call center can help you learn more, call them at&nbsp;<a href=\"tel: 1-833-814-8590\">1-833-814-8590</a>!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\",\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_shadow\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-very-light-gray-background-color has-background benefits__benefit_shadow\" id=\"prescriptions\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_title_shadow\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"benefits__benefit_title_shadow\">Prescriptions</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":198,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"benefits__benefit_image_shadow\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large benefits__benefit_image_shadow\"><img src=\"http://drivers-benefits.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/benefit-prescriptions.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-198\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Save up to 85% on prescription medications for you or a member of your family. Simply share your member ID number with your local pharmacy in person or over the phone. Provided by the&nbsp;<strong>Independent Drivers Guild.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li